  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The St JOSEPH'S HOSPITAL set up a fracture liaison service for osteopotic fracture. A
      specific nurse screens eligible patient admitted in emergency yard and call them to propose a
      bone densitometry and a medical coverage..

      The aim of the study is to evaluate this new organisation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
